<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>New Login to Photogram</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #fafafa;
            color: #262626;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 20px auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border: 1px solid #dbdbdb;
            border-radius: 8px;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(45deg, #405de6, #5851db, #833ab4, #c13584, #e1306c, #fd1d1d);
            padding: 30px 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .header h1 {
            color: #ffffff;
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 28px;
        }

        .content {
            padding: 40px 30px;
        }

        .content h2 {
            font-size: 22px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .info-box {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            border: 1px solid #e9ecef;
            border-radius: 6px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }

        .info-item {
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            font-size: 14px;
        }

        .info-label {
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #8e8e8e;
            width: 80px;
            display: inline-block;
        }

        .warning {
            color: #ed4956;
            font-size: 14px;
            margin-top: 20px;
            border-top: 1px solid #dbdbdb;
            padding-top: 20px;
        }

        .footer {
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #8e8e8e;
            border-top: 1px solid #dbdbdb;
        }

        .btn {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: #0095f6;
            color: #ffffff;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 4px;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>Photogram</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <h2>New Login Detected</h2>
            <p>Hi <%= name %>,</p>
            <p>We noticed a new login to your Photogram account. If this was you, you can safely ignore this email.</p>

            <div class="info-box">
                <div class="info-item"><span class="info-label">Time:</span>
                    <%= time %>
                </div>
                <div class="info-item"><span class="info-label">Device:</span> Web Browser</div>
            </div>

            <p>If this wasn't you, please secure your account immediately by resetting your password.</p>
            <a href="<%= frontend %>/auth/reset-password" class="btn">Secure Account</a>

            <div class="warning">
                <strong>Wasn't you?</strong> If you didn't log in, your account may have been compromised. Change your
                password right away to keep your photos safe.
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            <p>&copy; 2026 Photogram from Hamzah. All rights reserved.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>